#: src/diff.c:1023
msgid ""
"  These format options provide fine-grained control over the output\n"
"    of diff, generalizing -D/--ifdef."
msgstr ""
"  Dessa formatflaggor gör det möjligt att finjustera utskriften från\n"
"    diff, generaliserande -D/--ifdef."

